---
/**
 * /rutinas — Spanish keyword alias that permanently redirects to the canonical
 * /tdah landing page. Kept as a real route (not just a sitemap entry) so typed
 * or externally-linked "/rutinas" URLs resolve instead of 404-ing. Only /tdah
 * is listed in the sitemap, so search engines index a single canonical URL.
 */
return Astro.redirect("/tdah", 301);
---
